From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Spyros Seimenis <sse@edgeless.systems>
Date: Tue, 24 Feb 2026 11:43:16 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] QemuFwCfgAcpi: add AML device blocklist verification

Add ACPI blob verification that scans DSDT/SSDT AML bytecode for
Device() definitions and rejects blobs containing devices whose
NameSeg matches a blocklist. This provides a first line of defense
against injected ACPI devices from the host.

The blocklist currently contains "FAKE" as a proof-of-concept entry
to block the badaml-payload test device.

Signed-off-by: Spyros Seimenis <sse@edgeless.systems>
---
